title: Farm Employment, Hired Workers, Agricultural Marketing Service and Crop Reporting Board for United States
notes:
The Figures Refer To Employment During The Last Full Calendar Week Ending At Least One Day Before The End Of The Month. Source: U.S.Department Of Agriculture, Statistical Bulletin No236, "Farm Employment, " September 1958 (1940-57); "Farm Labor, " February 1959; March 1963, And Monthly Issues Thereafter. U.S.Department Of Agriculture, Agricultural Marketing Service, And Statistical Reporting Service, Crop Reporting Board.
